{
  "2244700": {
    "name": "Glasshouse",
    "steam_appid": 2244700,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/6b40534281f0023f898d61ad0401985b.avif?t=1767543345\" width=754 height=127 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Glasshouse</strong> 是一款设定在可怕世界大战前夕后资本主义 <strong>Feudalpunk</strong> 世界中的 <strong>回合制等距视角 CRPG</strong>。受 <strong>Disco Elysium</strong> 和 <strong>Pathologic</strong> 等 RPG 游戏的启发，Glasshouse 承诺带来一场<strong>紧张的叙事角色扮演体验</strong>，其中充满了令人难忘的角色、复杂的对话树、<strong>多重结局</strong>，以及超越屏幕的深刻意识形态反思。<br><br>你是 <strong>Wealdmaer</strong>，一位痴迷于被记住为“正义”领袖的公寓副主管。困在一个<strong>无法逃离的犯罪现场</strong>中，你需要处理 73B 宿舍那些可怜人的问题，存活于你的室友之间，并对抗一个将永远挑战你意识形态信仰的<strong>政治阴谋</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/1786bd6693f81b3543950cd59f476b39.poster.avif?t=1767543345\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/1786bd6693f81b3543950cd59f476b39.webm?t=1767543345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/a18bf03df4971ac44ca07abf6b654ccc.avif?t=1767543345\" width=754 height=127 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>副主管的职责</strong> - 你被困在公寓大楼里，身边有三具尸体和无数疑问。做好最坏的准备，你的邻居们的生命取决于你的选择！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>回合制战斗</strong> - 使用自制的即兴武器参与激动人心的战斗，或者选择和平之路，用你的口才让敌人投降。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>政治罗盘</strong> - 构建你的政治身份，磨练你的语言，克服模糊的意识形态技能检定。每个 NPC 都有自己的政治罗盘，细读每一次对话。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造你的出路</strong> - 通过阅读书籍获取新知识，并通过工作台制作临时装备！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一场戏剧性的戏剧</strong> - 受希腊悲剧启发，Glasshouse 由导演以一场不可避免的戏剧来叙述。在你的冒险过程中，你将由合唱团——自我的内心声音所陪伴。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lundonstoch 没有幸福的结局</strong> - 世界大战不可避免，用超过 8 个多重结局决定你要在 Glasshouse 的后资本主义世界中留下什么印记！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/c1ac608d906ae8994b4332b156bc6533.poster.avif?t=1767543345\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/c1ac608d906ae8994b4332b156bc6533.webm?t=1767543345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/afe5a7fe86795e17e5e299f756ff5f41.avif?t=1767543345\" width=754 height=127 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索 Lundonstoch 拥挤的工人阶级住宅</strong>，一个因惧怕即将到来的核打击而下令采取预防性封锁措施的封地。潜入你邻居的公寓，发现<strong>可怕的真相</strong>，做出无人敢做的选择。<strong>城市正在燃烧</strong>，但你只能从公寓楼的窗户看到它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着 <strong>隔离</strong>开始消磨 73B 宿舍居民的心智，一个政治阴谋使每个人的生命都处于危险之中。你能信任你的<strong>室友</strong>吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/98d09bb9b063cb05e148eb610437d4f2.poster.avif?t=1767543345\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/98d09bb9b063cb05e148eb610437d4f2.webm?t=1767543345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/2189a78e273cb4b835fe2e769849617a.avif?t=1767543345\" width=800 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glasshouse 的战斗受经典回合制战斗游戏 <strong>最终幻想</strong> 的启发，并加入了类似 <strong>Fear &amp; Hunger</strong> 的“解谜游戏”逻辑。每个回合，你可以选择攻击敌人或与其交谈。攻击需要<strong>掷骰子</strong>来对敌人的<strong>生命值</strong>造成伤害，而交谈则通过根据你的<strong>政治罗盘</strong>调整的对话线路提供调解途径。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/2c964cb5cbc6836420d8b03a7385adaf.poster.avif?t=1767543345\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/2c964cb5cbc6836420d8b03a7385adaf.webm?t=1767543345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">如果你能够“拨动”正确的心弦，你可以严重削弱他的<strong>威胁值</strong>。后者是一个整体数值，决定了你能在对手中引起的暗示程度：如果你的威胁值高于敌人，那么你可以尝试让他投降。游戏中没有小怪，<strong>每一场战斗都是一场 Boss 战</strong>，对手都有自己的动力、欲望和家庭。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/dc59d7b3918095ae2a4ae6ceced24d65.poster.avif?t=1767543345\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/dc59d7b3918095ae2a4ae6ceced24d65.webm?t=1767543345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/d918f325cc4d42cd2d7bf4fa8cff0026.avif?t=1767543345\" width=800 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有理想并不可耻，一切都是政治的，甚至是游戏玩法。在 Glasshouse 中，你可以获取观点点数并将其投资在<strong>政治罗盘</strong>上，这是一个<strong>基于五种不同意识形态的职业系统</strong>。打造你的政治构建，<strong>面对伦理困境</strong>，并尽力管理与你邻居的关系。<br><br>73B 宿舍的每位居民都有他自己的隐藏政治罗盘，通过对话来发现它，并<strong>按照你的意愿完成任务</strong>。<br><br>一切都有后果，小心不要<strong>引发风暴</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/886f371f9f750f311e161e49e8d4df83.poster.avif?t=1767543345\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/886f371f9f750f311e161e49e8d4df83.webm?t=1767543345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/f5c4c9b7f69e150a6f65828de0a6a731.avif?t=1767543345\" width=800 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glasshouse 的对话窗口是<strong>互动的迷宫</strong>。通过我们称之为<strong>“互动标签”</strong>的系统，在对话中导航，你可以发现自己陷入复杂的<strong>谜题</strong>、<strong>快速反应事件（QTE）</strong>、可收集的物品、秘密藏身处等等。借鉴经典的 TTRPG，我们创建了<strong>一个动态的对话系统</strong>，为不可预测的分支留有空间，<strong>游戏玩法始终处于核心</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/126845305c49b2829487486abf961dff.poster.avif?t=1767543345\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/126845305c49b2829487486abf961dff.webm?t=1767543345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每个对话都可能隐藏意想不到的互动，这要归功于<strong>狡诈机制</strong>，当你的库存中存在特定物品时，可以解锁新的对话线路。对话是任何优秀 CRPG 的核心，Glasshouse 通过当代的方式来致敬这一点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/010326d4fd4c3388f3267ca49429ac16.poster.avif?t=1767543345\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/010326d4fd4c3388f3267ca49429ac16.webm?t=1767543345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/eb036018286ebf768d66f2584b96a7c7.avif?t=1767543345\" width=754 height=127 /></span>Glasshouse 的世界是一个<strong>碎片化和去全球化的后资本主义世界</strong>。在 1828 年的来复枪罢工之后，国家和民族被拆除，取而代之的是<strong>封建地缘政治结构</strong>。这种突然的去国家化导致了<strong>技术进步的严重停滞</strong>，在接下来的 200 年里，促成了所谓的<strong>生产性封地</strong>和<strong>贫瘠封地</strong>之间巨大的经济鸿沟。<br><br>在 2028 年，由超过 52 个贫瘠封地组成的联盟 CoFoPo 宣布向现状宣战，目标是<strong>在资本主义旗帜下重新统一全球</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/7c4a5d88292ef28c7b83e6c3dae412d2.poster.avif?t=1767543345\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244700/extras/7c4a5d88292ef28c7b83e6c3dae412d2.webm?t=1767543345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
